metadata.name: Let's Go
metadata.description:
"Lets Go!" is a homage to the series "Bored Ape Muse" (BAM) .

BAM spans the calendar year of 2022. It is a collection laced with personal and public inspirations containing BAYC #6124 as the central muse. 

The 54-piece BAM collection is 1 of 1 ERC721 tokens minted on personal contract. 

This token gives green list access to to the first Bored Ape Muse collection dropping soon.

*This is the first artwork of 2023 (Signed and dated Ari Lankin 1.1.2023).

2000 x 6000 pixels, 600 DPI
